text:
I get a strange behaviour, after running tomcat few hours (some times days), it 
didn't response to any request (a  blank page is showed until connectionTimeout 
ocured). The load is about 15 requests/sec. 
SO : Linux SuSE 7.2;
VM: java 1.4.1
I used tomcat 4.0.6  FINAL HTTP Connector.
I try to also using tomcat 4.1.24 Coyote Connector but the same behaviour.

Also, what is strange there, an java process is "eating" al CPU resources on 
Linux machine, the process ID is 6344.

I saw that all threads of my application are still running but the tomcat 
didn't response.
